# Poem Generator


This project constructs a Vietnamese poem generator in the lục bát (six-eight) format, employing a Recurrent Neural Network (RNN) architecture with Bidirectional and Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) layers. The model is trained on "Truyen Kieu" data.

![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)


## I. Training Process




Training script:


```python

python train.py --epochs ${epochs}  --embedding-size ${embedding-size} --size-train ${psize-train}

```


Example:

```python

!python train.py --epochs 5 --embedding-size 100 --size-train 3250

``` 

There are some important arguments for the script you should consider when running it:

- `epochs`: The number of training iterations a model completes.
- `embedding-size`: The dimensionality of word representations in a language model.
- `size-train` : The total training data.
